Package: ustr.yc.interface
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve yields curves published by US Treasury (https://home.treasury.gov/)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Artur Wegrzyn
Maintainer: Artur Wegrzyn <awegrzyn17@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains set of functions for retrieving the yield 
    curves from the US Treasury website's Interest Rate statistics at
    https://home.treasury.gov/policy-issues/financing-the-government/interest-rate-statistics 
    Please note that only the nominal rates available in the 
    service indicated above are handled, i.e. "Daily Treasury Yield Curve Rates", 
    "Daily Treasury Bill Rates" and "Daily Treasury Long-Term Rates".
    Importantly, this package has data.table as one of its dependencies.
